    <title>Quivers and moduli of their thin sincere representations in Macaulay2</title>
    <summary>  We introduce the Macaulay2 package ThinSincereQuivers for studying acyclic
quivers, the moduli of their thin-sincere representations, and the reflexive
flow polytopes associated to them. We provide some background on the topic and
illustrate how the package recovers examples from the literature.
</summary>
